32 - Configuring a Wired Network Device
   route (print route table)
   ip addr (print IP)
   arp -a 
   ifconfig -a
   ifconfig eth* up
   ifocnfig eth* IP
   ifocnfig eth* netmask 255.255.255.0
   route add default gw IP   & routr del default
   

33 - Configuring Wireless Network Devices
